prompts.frontCover:
Flat 2D watercolor painting of a humorous thank-you card front. Features cartoon-illustrated versions of the young East Asian couple from the photo, who highly resemble their real-life counterparts. The woman, on the left, has long dark hair, glasses, and is smiling, wearing a light blue sweatshirt (logo omitted) and black pants. The man, standing behind her with his arms around her, has short dark hair, is smiling, and wears a tan hoodie and dark maroon pants. They are both looking at the viewer. They are depicted with slightly exaggerated, cute, chibi-style proportions to add to the lighthearted feel. The background is a simplified, artistic watercolor wash of a calm bay with a distant shoreline under a cloudy sky, evoking the scene from the photo. The style uses soft, flowing colors, visible brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture. Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Thanks for everything, Lao Lao!"

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
